Home has a brand new roof with a warranty, brand new windows and lots of upgrades throughout.  Come check out the backyard oasis!!! It is perfect for relaxation and outdoor activities! You will love the modern kitchen overlooking the living room area. Top of the line stainless appliances and beautiful granite countertops. But that’s not all - the seller is going above and beyond by paying for a temporary rate buy down, saving you thousands during your first 2 years of homeownership.
